Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:55.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Upper Yard" "Angel Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:02:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami's group on the Going Merry\Nheaded for the eastern shore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to escape from Upper Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Shandians headed\Nfor God's Shrine to defeat Eneru,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but encountered Priest Shura,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a great battle between\Nhim and Wyper took place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you throw your shield\Nand gun away?! Are you a fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he wouldn't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want a shoulder, you can have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Impact, huh?! Such things can't defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's ten times the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reject!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper! Are you trying to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try using the Reject Dial one more time!\NYour body'll be blown apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about my body?\NIsn't that called "resolve"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys can't be beaten\Nwithout any sacrifices like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least pray for everyone's good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, guys! Watch yourselves out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet at God's Shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At present, one has dropped out\Nof the Upper Yard survival game,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and eighty remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must not have had God's divine protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, four of the Straw Hats\Nset out to search for gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their goal: the ruins of an ancient city\Nwhere a vast amount of gold rests!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They head straight south\Nfrom the sacrificial altar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight... south...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fierce Midair Battle!\NPirate Zoro vs. Warrior Braham"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have nothing to say, nor do I\Nwant to hear any of your garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to eliminate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's nice and easy to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The priests and guerillas here all\Nuse strange fighting techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might be dangerous to use my\Nswords from the usual distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I need to defeat enemies\Nfrom a distance... I do have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other one might work\Nagainst small fries, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still needs work...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I'll try it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A flying slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shandians!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...should never have come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The forest has become quite lively...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a house away from the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, it's been swallowed by the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the ruins of\Nthe actual city are intact...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This route leads to God's Shrine!\NGoing any further would be insolent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to realize the\Nhistorical value that ruins have!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How impudent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have business with me?\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple! By God's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm to chop the Shandians\Nand you Blue Sea people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into pieces with this Axe Dial!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seis Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll teach you, Divine Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've killed many of our allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! These Divine Soldiers mean trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Right. Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that one of the Blue Sea\Npeople Wyper mentioned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guerilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems he wants to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno what brought this on, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, forgive me! I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:10:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up! I lose! Please don't kill me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! If you ain't a priest,\Ndon't be attackin' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! What the hell\Nare those flashing pistols?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. I underestimated you,\NBlue Sea person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had you pegged as a small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even step toward me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said there's all kinds of wavers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those skate things just another type?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using blasts to make himself float!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those pistols that flash each time he shoots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of those, I lose sight of him every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tiger...\N--Three swords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Blue Sea swordsman who\Ncan't even use wavers or dials...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you do is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know what this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Milky Dial!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aerial combat ain't just\Njumping around desperately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-An eel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet this'd make good eatin', broiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I really screwed up! Am I an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already dealing with a\Nnimble enough bastard here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but then I get my leg shot up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything I can do\Nabout those flashing pistols?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some mighty nice\Nweapons you got there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But too bad! Look! I have goggles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your flashing pistols\Nwon't work on me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't look like sunglasses to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He saw through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem fond of these Flash Guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close distance is vital to a swordsman.\NYou're no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you guys are here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as you are here,\Nyou're still our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now die already! Your leg\Nmust hurt pretty bad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business. It only grazed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting shot while gawking at\Nan eel is proof I still lack vigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, this is the perfect\Nsituation to try out that technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eyes, ears, nose, tongue, body, mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those six roots of man\Nhave good, evil, and peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And each of those has pure and impure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,36 worldly desires in a lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now have the barrel of\Na cannon pointed at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have pistols, I have a cannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance and power-wise,\Nmy weapon is superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but now you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gone mad?\NWhere is this weapon of yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever seen a flying slash?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Single-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-six Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:18:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing personal, but I ain't the\Ntype of guy who'll die when told to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept this survival challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost all sense of direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Zoro! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to be left here to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I go to heaven if I die?\NWill the doctor be waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't think like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a doctor! I can't think\Nabout death so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder what heaven is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, isn't this heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things turned all ruin-ish at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the others are here!\NI guess I really am great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Could I be the first one here?!\NYeah! My nose must've helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I'm the first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A raccoon dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't work on me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-kun!\N--H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened?! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I can't hear his heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a foolish man. And I didn't\Neven come here to bring you harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cold-hearted hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly been six long years,\NFormer God Gan Fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Racing full speed ahead as always
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A to Z, we run through it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all have worries and fall many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we just need to rise to the top someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could be beyond the sea\Nin which the morning sun rises?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go little by little toward\Nthe brilliantly shining sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never treat you "bad"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times did we fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, we're definitely\Npointing at tomorrow now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile! Come back to you, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to you, friends\NCome back to you, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to you, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to you, friends\NCome back to you, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to you, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Sanji-kun is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it just you and the old\Nman here?! I can't rely on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! I'm going to eliminate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.99,0:23:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! Your bazooka doesn't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wretched pest! Don't mock sky combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
